{"tid":1937371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位多多探望沙嶺手足⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-03-22T00:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T20:02:15.000Z","uid":263323,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9f13c9b23d75cef9a605da863687e6be2ee85f76","tid":1937371,"uid":263323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T00:33:56.000Z","msg":"AP同恐怖在線去咗沙嶺拜祭，燒咗好多金銀衣紙俾手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n法師話義士想我哋多啲人去探佢哋<br />\n等佢哋知道我哋無忘記佢哋<br />\n咁樣佢哋會容易啲放下，可以安息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都可以去燒多啲金銀衣紙俾佢哋<br />\n等佢哋多啲能量或者可以報夢話俾屋企人知<br />\n睇到我喊晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cRqjYeJ6zOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcRqjYeJ6zOg&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=4cbb7c0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cRqjYeJ6zOg</a><br />\n<br />\n恐怖在線個邊揾到高靈人士睇現場<br />\n話佢哋好孤單，心事未了<br />\n唔明白點解自己會死，點解會葬咗係沙嶺<br />\n因為明明佢哋有屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話佢哋唔會安息⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇返要課金⋯⋯大家可以支持下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rA6Txze.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrA6Txze.png&h=68529cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家以後清明都去探下手足啦<br />\n記得帶少少嘢俾佢哋，等佢哋多啲能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋一定唔可以忘記佢哋！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"22150bd08db6abb96a610adc7380d61c2342d1d0","tid":1937371,"uid":263323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T00:35:01.000Z","msg":"自推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5ed4a50cefc202d00aaf4d87ee89c88fcf8a52","tid":1937371,"uid":247421,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T00:44:14.000Z","msg":"我諗佢地需要既係伸冤平反,<br />\n之後就可以安息."},{"pid":"12f9357156fafa69c57827eb2f7edca8d7be65d7","tid":1937371,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T00:44:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2db279554e77c34b44f8bcfeb3a6606422a84f5a","tid":1937371,"uid":136400,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T00:44:52.000Z","msg":"推，希望有人可以幫手搵番逝世手足家人"},{"pid":"b3e69c4c0c0b46227730e94e6a823af96e7c4fa6","tid":1937371,"uid":263323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f5ed4a50cefc202d00aaf4d87ee89c88fcf8a52","tid":1937371,"uid":247421,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T00:44:14.000Z","msg":"我諗佢地需要既係伸冤平反,<br />\n之後就可以安息."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T00:46:31.000Z","msg":"當然，我哋要完成佢哋未完成嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81252008e300f877f627eab3704c1484b79cc764","tid":1937371,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T00:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98aee2a6e0ab979689a2e499789e339ed73b07e6","tid":1937371,"uid":258948,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T00:58:44.000Z","msg":"可以啊，但想知邊啲係手足既墓？coz全部得數字...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10758e9aa00abef4ac9774f1cfc8b4b27a1814c","tid":1937371,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T01:00:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Zt9P_1o_e0Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZt9P_1o_e0Q&d=HaOdb